description:
The Xtra Factor UK - Season 12, Special Episodes 1 & 2




Brand new X Factor hosts Olly Murs and Caroline Flack talk through their hand-picked top ten moments from the X Factor archives. Presented by Rochelle Humes and Melvin Odoom.

Brand new X Factor judges Nick Grimshaw and Rita Ora look back over the past eleven series of the singing competition and count down their favourite moments.




Original Air Dates: 22-Aug-2015 & 23-Aug-2015
